{"tid":2276851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水連線放映會 警監視查身份證","createTime":"2020-11-08T05:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T05:30:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c0ef106aff112b718a050b010a69715814ea39","tid":2276851,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/IX2RB2E3BZCLJC2YZTCAIMNGQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FIX2RB2E3BZCLJC2YZTCAIMNGQY%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft220Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=b8218859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FIX2RB2E3BZCLJC2YZTCAIMNGQY%2F&h=475c4ac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/IX2RB2E3BZCLJC2YZTCAIMNGQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n天水連線放映會 警監視查身份證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iMitIokhwZOZoEUy8sGb6frPD10=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GMDE6NH5TVGXJEALGCD5FGG22E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiMitIokhwZOZoEUy8sGb6frPD10%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGMDE6NH5TVGXJEALGCD5FGG22E.jpg&h=b0316f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批警員到場監視，並登記天水連線成員身份證。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社區組織天水連線昨晚7時在天水圍銀座廣場外空地舉行紀錄片《刑．暴．誌》放映會，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPTU戒備 指違限聚令<br />\n<br />\n警方昨下午6時起，已派遣至少兩架衝鋒車到場戒備，其後至少10名軍裝警員到空地駐守並到廣場巡邏，更安排大量便衣警和機動部隊警員在附近公園隱身觀察。放映會開始後，有十多人保持社交距離站立觀看影片，警方至少五次以擴音器警告在場市民違反限聚令，要求聚集市民散開，有剛到場觀片的家長立即帶小孩離開，放映會至晚上近8時完結。<br />\n<br />\n郭小姐和曾先生特意到場觀看放映會，郭小姐說，這些影片要「夾時間」和地點才可以看到，所以特意前來。他們批評警方高調巡邏旨在嚇走市民，「佢哋唔喺度就天下太平」。曾先生則說：「如果今日咁嘅態度應付7.21咪好囉，咪唔會有話柄囉！」<br />\n<br />\n天水連線成員、區議員林進及兩個助手在現場被警方登記身份證，其後獲放行。他表示，影片講述數名社運人士體驗中國式酷刑，內容十分有意義，認為一旦香港淪陷，不知道港人會否有一天遭受酷刑，影片彷彿給港人心理準備。他亦指現時不能舉行遊行集會，放映會讓大家記住一年來走過的路，提醒香港人還有同路人在堅持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f6MufQVwHRTbU1jZX9OrLHmSr-w=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CMUN6KX3HBBWHMAOPDDWJEHWCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff6MufQVwHRTbU1jZX9OrLHmSr-w%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCMUN6KX3HBBWHMAOPDDWJEHWCI.jpg&h=2f74d8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名中年男街坊訓斥警員，指警方知法犯法。"}]}